data.description:
Coming Soon - Great 3 Bedroom Townhouse! - Welcome home to this great end unit townhouse on a quiet cul-de-sac, with a convenient Northwest location.  Amenities are include a community pool, clubhouse, tennis courts, and landscaping too! This home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a 2 car garage.  Includes fireplace, washer, dryer, fridge, and air conditioning. Pets acceptable on approval.  

Besides living in this awesome unit, you will also get to work with an AMAZING management team!

Join us!
Step 1- Come check it out! To view it, simply stop by our office and check out a set of keys. We are located at 305 W. Moana Ste C (Downstairs). We take a copy of your ID, and require a $20 key deposit. 

If you like what you see, then you move on to...
Step 2!- Fill out this application! (copy the link in your browser)

Interested in our other rentals? Take a look at them here (copy the link in your browser) :
http
www.gandolfoteam.com/rent.html

We look forward to having you as our tenant.
Cheers!

PS- If you are interested in seeing if home ownership might be right for you, we can also help you on the journey to own! Reach out to find out how we can help get you qualified for a home.

(RLNE4799197)
